The output type of the CASE WHEN seems different for each THEN/ELSE branch.

{noformat}
CASE WHEN (cint is not null) THEN (cint) WHEN (cfloat is not null) THEN (cfloat) WHEN (csmallint is not null) THEN (csmallint) ELSE (null) END
{noformat}

The patch doesn't vectorized the vertex anymore and has this message:

{noformat}
notVectorizedReason: SELECT operator: Unable to vectorize CASE WHEN expression -- data type float of THEN/ELSE expression is different than the result type string. Conversion is not supported
{noformat}
